summary: An Ordinance providing for the condemnation and appropriation of a portion of the Northwest Quarter (N.W. 1/4) and of the Northeast Quarter (N.E. 1/4) of the Southwest Quarter (S.W. 1/4) of Section Nine (9), Township Twenty-five (25) North, Range Four (4), W. M., in the City of Seattle, for park and parkway purposes.
